    "description": "<strong>Castle Rain</strong> is a 3D top-down action game where you control <strong>Billy</strong>, a mushroom whose island has been devastated by a villain who turned his friends and everyone around into manipulated zombies. Now, Billy must race against time to stop the dreaded villain Dr. Clamp. Escape, hide, shoot enemies, find weapons, and protect yourself from projectiles in this cartoon-style top-down adventure.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050810/extras/Frame_47.png?t=1719603083\" /></span><br><br><strong>Cure the Enemies</strong><br><br>You can destroy zombie enemies or bring them to your side by healing them with an injection. They will then fight alongside you, attacking other zombies and unhealed enemies.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050810/extras/Twitter_header_-_8.png?t=1719603083\" /></span><br><br><strong>Protect Yourself</strong><br><br>You can protect yourself in places and kill everyone who enters your base.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050810/extras/Twitter_header_-_9.png?t=1719603083\" /></span>",
